body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello! Thank you for contacting our Car Dealership customer service. My name is Jason Richardson. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Denise. How can I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I am feeling really frustrated. My car was supposed to be shipped two weeks ago, and I still haven't received any updates.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I apologize for the delay, Denise. To help me locate your order, could you please provide me with your order number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, my order number is seven eight nine four five.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Denise. I have noted down your order number. Could you also provide me with the primary phone number associated with your account?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: My phone number is five five five eight nine zero one two three four.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for sharing that information, Denise. I will investigate the status of your order and follow up with you shortly. Thank you for your patience.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for your time, Denise. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, that's all. Thank you for your help.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: You're welcome, Denise. Have a great day.
